Package: deepnnet
Title: Deep Neural Networks for Tabular Classification and Regression
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Imad", "EL BADISY", email = "elbadisyimad@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Imad EL BADISY [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Imad EL BADISY <elbadisyimad@gmail.com>
Description: Fit multilayer perceptrons for tabular classification and
    regression using 'torch'. The package provides formula interface,
    automatic preprocessing for numeric and categorical predictors, early
    stopping, prediction, task-aware metrics, tuning, training-history plots,
    and permutation importance. Neural network training is implemented with
    the R package 'torch' by Falbel and Luraschi (2025)
    <doi:10.32614/CRAN.package.torch>.
URL: https://github.com/ielbadisy/mlp
BugReports: https://github.com/ielbadisy/mlp/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
